<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>{{ .title }}</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      background-color: #151920;
      font-family: Consolas, monaco, monospace;
      margin: 40px auto;
      max-width: 650px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #EAEBE6;
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    a,
    h1 {
      color: #3bb13b;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3 {
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <h1>{{ .title }}</h1>
    <aside>An autogenerated TODO list for my public commitments.</aside>
  </header>
  <h2>Alpine Linux aports</h2>
  <ul>
    {{ range $name, $versions := .alpineTasks }}
    <li>package <span style="color:red">{{ $name }}</span> out-of-date, want: <span style="color:#3bb13b">{{ index $versions 0 }}</span>, have: <span style="color:red">{{ index
      $versions 1 }}</span></li>
    {{ end }}
  </ul>
  <hr>
  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>I (<a href="https://bio.markpash.me/">markpash</a>) created this so that I can keep up with my public commitments,
    such as the packages I maintain, services I host and software I write.</p>
  <p>At time of you reading this, this site only generates TODO list items from out-of-date Alpine Linux packages that I
    maintain. Other functionality may be added later.</p>
</body>

</html>